divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing outside when I seen a fireball in the sky so I ran inside the house to grab my Iphone and I came back out and took photos of this object as it was flying away from me at a steady rate. to my surprise there was another object over my house and I took photos of that one as it was flying away from me. I have the photos!!!
